test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x74989017de00>([-61])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x74989017de00> = [[1, -61], [1, -61, 1], [-61], [-61, 1], [1, -61], [1, -61, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 61 == -61
 +  where 61 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -61])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
